# Generated eval artifacts (counts snapshots, pre-label JSONL, verify sheets,
# verified labels) are reproducible from the runner and may contain real
# application data (JD text, email subjects/snippets). Keep them ALL out of git
# — this is a PUBLIC repo. The directory itself is tracked via .gitkeep so the
# runner has a place to write.
*.json
*.jsonl
*.xlsx
*.csv
!.gitkeep
